definition: "to eat" or "food" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 184)
to feed (a child, domestic animal etc)/to keep/to raise (an animal)

sentences.english: Both men had direct contact with dead chickens when feeding carcasses to their dogs.
sentences.chinese: 這兩名男子均在將死雞屍體餵狗時直接接觸了死雞。

sentences.english: He then brings her heart home to feed his dog.
sentences.chinese: 隨後他將屍體的心臟帶回家餵狗。

sentences.english: Weiwei is bored with watermelon, so I intend to make some change.
sentences.chinese: 吃了幾天的西瓜，我打算換些喫的餵它。

sentences.english: The trial showed that lactating goats can be feeded with whole corn or coarsely cracked corn instead of deeply processed corn.
sentences.chinese: 說明對泌乳羊可採用整粒或粗粉的形式投餵玉米。

sentences.english: Did you remember to feed the dog?
She scraped with a spoon to feed me apple.
sentences.chinese: 她用勺子把蘋果刮下來餵我喫。

sentences.english: The results of the study can contribute to the promotion of breastfeeding.
sentences.chinese: 本研究結果可爲提升母奶哺餵措施提供指引。

sentences.english: To avoid overfeeding, consider giving your dog low- or reduced-fat dairy products.
sentences.chinese: 爲了不至於餵過量，可以考慮使用低脂奶製品。

sentences.english: The decline in breastfeeding has become a major concern to health workers.
sentences.chinese: 母乳哺餵率下降之關注議題已經考量到職場員工。

sentences.english: Breastfeeding pamphlets are available in our hospital to help you.
sentences.chinese: 本院提供之母乳育嬰資料對你餵哺母乳有極大的幫助。

sentences.english: So will the demand-feeding the baby life without law?
sentences.chinese: 那麼按需餵哺會不會使寶寶生活沒有規律呢？

sentences.english: Have your partner feed you grapes.
sentences.chinese: 讓你的另一半餵你喫葡萄吧。

sentences.english: Mrs. Arable gave him a feeding around noontime each day, Fern was away in school.
sentences.chinese: 弗恩上學的時候，就由阿拉布爾太太每天中午餵它。

sentences.english: By contrast, normal mice fed the same diet gain very modestamounts of weight.
sentences.chinese: 相比之下，餵了同樣食物的正常老鼠體重增加相當少。

sentences.english: I watched the carps in the pond and fed them some bread that I had brought with me.
sentences.chinese: 我觀賞池裏的鯉魚並用我帶來的一些麪包餵它們。

sentences.english: A child was feeding the peahen in the zoo.
sentences.chinese: 一個孩子正在餵動物園裏的那隻雌孔雀。
